	  <div id="side"> <!-- Block of text on left side of page -->
	    <div style="text-align: center">JMRI&reg; is...</div>
	    <dl>
		<dt><h3><a href="DecoderPro/index.shtml">DecoderPro&reg;</a></h3></dt>
		<dd>
		    A better tool for programming decoders.
		    DecoderPro simplifies the job of configuring complicated DCC decoders
		    by providing screens on which you can select the various options and
		    values you want.
		</dd>

		<dt><h3><a href="PanelPro/PanelPro.shtml">PanelPro&trade;</a></h3></dt>
		<dd>
		    Designing and Operating CRT based CTC control panels that reflect the real-time
		    state of your railroad <em>and</em> let you control it - almost like
		    a Prototype dispatcher!
		</dd>

		<dt><h3><a href="../tools/index.shtml">General Tools</a></h3></dt>
		<dd>JMRI provides powerful tools for working with your
		layout.
		    <UL>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/throttle/ThrottleMain.shtml">Throttles</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/consisttool/ConsistTool.shtml">Consisting</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/signaling/index.shtml">Signals</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/Lights.shtml">Lights</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/Routes.shtml">Routes</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/Logix.shtml">Logix</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/fastclock/index.shtml">Fast Clocks</a>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/speedometer/index.shtml">Speedometer</a> &amp;<BR>
		    <a href="../tools/speedometer/SpeedMatch.shtml">Engine Speed Matching</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/scripting/index.shtml">Scripting</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../hardware/PDA.shtml">PDA access</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="LocoTools/index.shtml">LocoNet tools</a></dfn>
		    </UL>
		</dd>

		<dt><h3><a href="../tools/automation/">Layout Automation</a></h3></dt>
		<dd>JMRI can be used to automate parts 
		of your layout, from simply controlling a crossing gate
		to running trains in the background.
		    <UL>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/signaling/index.shtml">Signaling</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="../tools/scripting/index.shtml">Scripting</a></dfn>
		    </UL>
		</dd>
		
		<dt><h3><a href="../../package/jmri/jmrit/operations/Operations.shtml">OperationsPro&trade;</a></h3></dt>
		<dd>JMRI's operations program can generate train manifests and car switch lists for your model railroad.
		</dd>

		<div style="clear: both"></div>
